dc_title_s: Floridae Americae provinciae: recens and exactissima descriptio; auctore Jacobo le Moyne.
dc_description_s: To accompany Le Moyne's narrative 979 F6L. Reproduction, probably late 19th cent. 1 map; 37 x 46 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
